    "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you first acquire this Skill, choose a gadget type: <strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.SsR6UJXT65Q1qNO2]{Alchemy}, @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.1tfYFkiXLuTOUmre]{Infusion}</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>, </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">or <strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.EmwWSYlFjlUSGPLL]{Magitech} </strong>(<strong>Core Rulebook</strong>, page <strong>212</strong>). You gain its </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>basic benefits</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Whenever you take this Skill again, choose one option: you gain the </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>basic benefits</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">of a new gadget type; </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>OR</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">you gain the </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>advanced benefits</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">of a gadget type whose </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>basic benefits</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">you already obtained; </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>OR </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">you gain the </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>superior benefits</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">of a gadget type whose </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>advanced benefits</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">you already obtained.</span> </p>",
